y lost three Grand Slam finals to Federer - and one to Djokovic.Murray battered Djokovic in the final of the US Open to finally end his wait for the accolade he desired above all other.Andy Murray has won two Olympic gold medals throughout his tennis career|PAIn 2013, Murray got the better of the same opponent to finally win Wimbledon.And his last major came eight years ago, with Murray overcoming Milos Raonic in straight sets to win his second Wimbledon crown.\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 3462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1828, \"end\": 1832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/More_(command)\", \"score\": 0.9401799466284023, \"rank\": 0.04993065187240515, \"text\": \"MORE\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/More_(command)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/More_(command)\"}, {\"begin\": 1833, \"end\": 1837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.734210053509759, \"rank\": 0.16307907180328124, \"text\": \"Luke\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luke_Snyder\"}, {\"begin\": 1996, \"end\": 2009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roger Federer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\"}, {\"begin\": 2049, \"end\": 2054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.8976587531794437, \"rank\": 0.11399733194511742, \"text\": \"Swiss\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 2119, \"end\": 2133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"